  "summary": [
    "Use one shared official-letter number and date for every new complaint letter until an operator changes them",
    "Initialize the shared reference from the most recently finalized letter so the current office number and date are preserved",
    "Allow the same printed letter number across different complaint letters while retaining UUID, complaint and revision audit identity",
    "Persist changes made on the configuration page or when a customized letter is finalized",
    "Use the same shared number and date for all letters generated in a bulk formal-letter batch",
    "Remove the misleading global unique-number control from the user interface",
    "Run complete tests and Astro build by default with database-first automatic rollback"
